{"product_id":"rules-breaker-bottoms","title":"RULES BREAKER BOTTOMS","description":"\u003cp\u003e 420 GSM COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e BIO-WASHED MATTE FINISH\u003cbr\u003e PREMIUM 100% COTTON MATERIAL\u003cbr\u003e “RULES BREAKER” HIGH-DENSITY SCREEN PRINT\u003cbr\u003e YKK ZIPPER POCKETS FOR SECURE STORAGE\u003cbr\u003e STRAIGHT BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eUltra-heavy 420 GSM cotton fleece delivers superior weight, warmth, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eCrafted for a structured yet comfortable feel suitable for everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBold “Rules Breaker” screen print on the right leg for a striking visual statement.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eCombed, bio-washed finish enhances softness while maintaining long-lasting color depth.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eHigh-quality YKK zipper pockets provide secure and functional storage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette designed for relaxed movement and modern streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft hand feel with a premium matte finish for elevated comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eVersatile essential that balances function, comfort, and attitude.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eSweatpants constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial and durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for relaxed, all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for diverse body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waistband for adjustable fit and ease of wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for added utility.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey construction ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885007622298,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885007655066,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885007687834,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885007720602,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885007753370,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885007786138,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_5554_1__11zon_6ecb50a5-1cb7-47a5-a10a-199c25570951.webp?v=1768930693","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/rules-breaker-bottoms","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}